{
  "chapter": "034",
  "title": "燕召公世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "召公封燕",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公奭</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>同姓，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姬氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>掉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>以后，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span>在北<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "召公辅佐成王",
      "text": "在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>位列<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公</span>：从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陕</span>以西的地区，由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>主管；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陕</span>以东的地区，由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>主管。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>年幼，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>摄理政务，当国执政，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>对此有所疑虑，便作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">君奭</span>。<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">君奭</span>中流露出对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>的不满。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>于是称述：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>时有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>，感通<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">皇天</span>；在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太戊</span>时，则有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊陟</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臣扈</span>，感通<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">上帝</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">巫咸</span>治理<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>家；在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖乙</span>时，则有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">巫贤</span>；在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武丁</span>时，则有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">甘般</span>：这些贤臣皆有功业记载，维护保全了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>朝。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>才心悦。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "甘棠遗爱",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>治理<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西方</span>，深得百姓的和悦。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>巡行乡里城邑，遇有<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">棠树</span>，就在树下判决诉讼、处理政事，从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">伯</span>到平民各得其所，无人失其本分。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>去世后，民众思念<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>的政绩，怀念那<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">棠树</span>而不敢砍伐，并作歌颂扬，作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">甘棠</span>之诗。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "惠侯在位",
      "text": "从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>以下经<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九世</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕惠侯</span>当时正值<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周厉王</span>奔逃到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彘</span>、<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">共和</span>行政的时期。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "5.1": {
      "title": "釐侯至顷侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐侯</span>即位。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周宣王</span>刚即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十一年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑桓公</span>初封于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">顷侯</span>即位。"
    },
    "5.2": {
      "title": "顷侯时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">顷侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周幽王</span>淫乱无道，被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">犬戎</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>杀。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>开始列为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "5.3": {
      "title": "哀侯至缪侯",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">顷侯</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">哀侯</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郑侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十六年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪侯</span>即位。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "缪侯至庄公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">缪侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲁隐公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十八年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓侯</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓侯</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄公</span>即位。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "7.1": {
      "title": "庄公时代",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span>开始称霸。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>攻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周惠王</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周惠王\">惠王（周惠王）</span>出奔到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">温</span>，诸侯<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周惠王\">惠王（周惠王）</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王子穨\">穨（王子穨）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">周王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十七年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>国拘执了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲父</span>而将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周惠王\">惠王（周惠王）</span>送入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十七年</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">山戎</span>来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵</span>犯我国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span>前来救援<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，于是向北<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>击<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">山戎</span>而回师。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕君</span>送<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐桓公</span>出境，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>便把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>君所至之处的土地割让给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>按<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成周</span>时的职分共同向<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>进贡；让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>重修<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>之<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十三年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">襄公</span>即位。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "8.1": {
      "title": "襄公至桓公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">襄公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋文公</span>举行<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">践土</span>之会，称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">伯</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十一年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">殽</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span>北。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦穆公</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">襄公</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>即位。"
    },
    "8.2": {
      "title": "桓公至武公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十六年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十五年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武公</span>即位。这一年<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了三<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郤</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>。"
    },
    "8.3": {
      "title": "武公至惠公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十九年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">懿公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">懿公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">崔杼</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>杀其国君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄公</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠公</span>即位。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "9.1": {
      "title": "惠公出奔齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高止</span>来投奔。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠公</span>宠姬众多，想要去除诸位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>而立宠姬<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>们共同<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀了姬<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宋</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠公</span>恐惧，奔逃到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高偃</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国，请求共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，送<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕君</span>回国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋平公</span>允许，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，送<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠公</span>回国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">惠公</span>到达<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>就死了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>人<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼公</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "10.1": {
      "title": "悼公至献公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">共公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平公</span>即位。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国公室衰微，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六卿</span>开始强大。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">平公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十八年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吴王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖闾</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国攻入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十九年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">献公</span>即位。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵鞅</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">围</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">范</span>氏、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中行</span>氏于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">朝歌</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">献公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田常</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">弑</span>杀其国君<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简公</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">献公</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝公</span>即位。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "11.1": {
      "title": "三晋灭知伯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">知伯</span>，瓜分其地，三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>强盛。"
    },
    "11.2": {
      "title": "孝公至釐公",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝公</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十六年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">湣公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">湣公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十一年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐公</span>即位。这一年，三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>正式列为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "12.1": {
      "title": "釐公至文公",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">林营</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">釐公</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>即位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>即位。这一年，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦献公</span>去世。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>日益强盛。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "13.1": {
      "title": "文公与苏秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十九年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐威王</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>初次前来谒见，游说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>赠以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>，让他到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵肃侯</span>采纳了他的主张。于是约<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>合纵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">从长</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦惠王</span>把自己的女儿嫁给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>为妻。"
    },
    "13.2": {
      "title": "文公卒易王立",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十九年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>去世，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>即位，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">易王</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "14.1": {
      "title": "易王与苏秦之乱",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">易王</span>刚即位时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐宣王</span>趁着<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国居丧<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>攻我国，夺取了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十城</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国，使它归还<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十城</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕君</span>称<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕文公</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>私通，害怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，便游说<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>派他出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国作反间，想借此扰乱<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">易王</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>去世，其子<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬哙\">哙（姬哙）</span>即位。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "15.1": {
      "title": "燕哙即位与子之擅权",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬哙\">哙（姬哙）</span>即位后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>时，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>结为姻亲，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>也与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>交好。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>死后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣王</span>又任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕哙</span>三年，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，不<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span>而退。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>相，权重位尊，独断国政。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>问道：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王怎么样？\" 回答说：\"必定不能称霸。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>问：\"为什么？\" 回答说：\"不信任他的大臣。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>想以此激励<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>来尊宠<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>大加信任。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>因而赠送<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏代</span>百<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>，任凭他指使。"
    },
    "15.2": {
      "title": "燕哙让位子之",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鹿毛寿</span>对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>说：\"不如把国家让给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>。人们之所以称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤者</span>，是因为他把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">许由</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">许由</span>没有接受，这样<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>便有让<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>之名而实际上没有失去<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>。如今王把国家让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>必定不敢接受，这样王就与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的德行相同了。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>因而把国家托付给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>权势大盛。又有人说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>推荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>，过后任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>的心腹做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吏</span>。等到年老，认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>的人不足以担当<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>之事，就传位给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>。过后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>和他的党羽<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">夺</span>取了天下。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>都说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>名义上传<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>，实际上却是让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>自取。如今王说把国家托付给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>，而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吏</span>员没有一个不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>的人，这是名义上托付给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>而实际上是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>执政。\" 王就收回<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百石</span>以上<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吏</span>员的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>信，交给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>南面而行王事，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬哙\">哙（姬哙）</span>年老不再过问政事，反而居于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>位，国事全由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>决断。"
    },
    "15.3": {
      "title": "国乱齐伐燕",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>，国家大乱，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>恐慌。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">市被</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕昭王\">平（燕昭王）</span>密谋，准备<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸将</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐湣王</span>说：\"趁此机会出兵，必定<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王就派人对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕昭王\">平（燕昭王）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>听说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>的义举，将要废除私心而伸张公理，整饬君臣之义，申明父子之位。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>之国小，不足以为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>前驱或后援。即便如此，一切听从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>差遣。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>于是联结党羽、聚集众人，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">市被</span>围攻<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">公宫</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>，没能攻<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">克</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">市被</span>和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>反过来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕昭王\">平（燕昭王）</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">市被</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>，尸身示众。于是构乱数月，死者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众人</span>恐慌，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>离心。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孟轲</span>对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>王说：\"如今<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，这是与文王、武王同样的机会，不可错过。\" 王便命令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">章子</span>率领五都之兵，加上北地的军队<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>不战，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">城门</span>不闭，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬哙\">哙（姬哙）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>大<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">胜</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>逃亡<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">二年（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>人共同<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕昭王\">平（燕昭王）</span>为王，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕昭王\">昭王（燕昭王）</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "16.1": {
      "title": "昭王卑身求贤",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕昭王</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span>之后即位，以谦卑之礼和厚重财礼招揽<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤者</span>。对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郭隗</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>乘着<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤</span>国大乱<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">袭</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤</span>深知<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国小力弱，不足以报仇。然而若能得到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贤士</span>共治国家，来雪先<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>之耻，正是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤</span>的愿望。先生看有谁合适，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孤</span>愿亲身侍奉他。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郭隗</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>如果一定要招致<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，就<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">先从隗始</span>。何况比<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郭隗\">隗（郭隗）</span>更贤能的人，岂会嫌<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>之远呢？\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕昭王\">昭王（燕昭王）</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：郭隗\">隗（郭隗）</span>改建<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宫</span>室而以师礼事奉他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">邹衍</span>自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国来，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">剧辛</span>自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国来，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人争相奔赴<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>吊唁死者、慰问孤寡，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>同甘苦。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "17.1": {
      "title": "乐毅破齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国殷实富足，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士卒</span>乐于奋勇作战，于是任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将军</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>、三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>合谋<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span>逃亡在外。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>兵独自追击败军，一直攻入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临淄</span>，尽<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝</span>物，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">烧</span>毁了其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宫室</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宗庙</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国城邑未攻下的，只剩<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">聊</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span>，其余都归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，如此<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>。"
    },
    "17.2": {
      "title": "昭王卒惠王立",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕昭王\">昭王（燕昭王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十三年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕惠王\">惠王（燕惠王）</span>即位。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "18.1": {
      "title": "惠王疑乐毅齐田单复国",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕惠王\">惠王（燕惠王）</span>做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>时，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>有嫌隙；即位以后，怀疑<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乐毅\">毅（乐毅）</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骑劫</span>代他为将。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐毅</span>逃亡<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田单</span>以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">即墨</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>军，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骑劫</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>兵退回，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国全部收复旧有城邑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐湣王\">湣王（齐湣王）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">死</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">莒</span>，于是立其子为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐襄王\">襄王（齐襄王）</span>。"
    },
    "18.2": {
      "title": "惠王卒武成王立",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕惠王\">惠王（燕惠王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>去世。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">燕武成王</span>即位。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "19.1": {
      "title": "武成王时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武成王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田单</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>我国，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中阳</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四十</span>余万。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武成王</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝王</span>即位。"
    },
    "19.2": {
      "title": "孝王时期",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">围</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>者<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">解</span>去。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬喜\">喜（姬喜）</span>即位。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "20.1": {
      "title": "今王喜伐赵大败",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬喜\">喜（姬喜）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭王（秦昭王）</span>去世。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>命令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗腹</span>前往结好<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，以五百<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">赵王</span>祝酒。回来报告<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">赵王</span>的壮年人都死于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长平</span>，他们的遗孤尚未长大，可以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>攻。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>召见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">昌国君</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>询问。回答说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国是四面都要作战的<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">之国</span>，其民习于兵事，不可<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>攻。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>说：\"我以五倍兵力去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>攻一倍之敌。\" 回答说：\"不可。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>大怒，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>都认为可以。最终起<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">二军</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千乘</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗腹</span>率军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄗</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卿</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>。唯独<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">将渠</span>对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>说：\"与人通关结好，以五百<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>祝他国之<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>之酒，使者回来就反过来<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击他，不祥，兵不会成功。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>不听，亲自率偏军随后出征。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">将渠</span>拉住<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">绶</span>带劝阻道：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>一定不要亲自前去，去了不会成功。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>用脚踢开他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">将渠</span>哭泣说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>不是为自己，是为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>啊！\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>军到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宋子</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>为将，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">击破</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗腹</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄗</span>。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">卿</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">代</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐间</span>出奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>追击<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百</span>余里，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>都。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>人请和，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人不许，一定要<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">将渠</span>主持议和。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>相<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">将渠</span>出面议和。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>听从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">将渠</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">解</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>之围。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "21.1": {
      "title": "秦并诸国之势",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>东<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>，设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三川郡</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">榆次</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十七城</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大原郡</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">秦王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">政（秦始皇）</span>初即位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>率军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">繁阳</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>之。赵<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝成王</span>去世，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼襄王</span>即位。派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>代<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>不服从，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乐乘</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>奔<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武遂</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">方城</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">剧辛</span>原居<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞暖</span>交好，后来逃亡<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">走</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>屡次被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>所困，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>离去，令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞暖</span>为将，想趁<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>疲敝<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击它。问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">剧辛</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">剧辛</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞暖</span>容易对付。\" <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">剧辛</span>率军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞暖</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>之，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>军<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二万</span>人，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">剧辛</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十城</span>，设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东郡</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鄴</span>等<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九城</span>。赵<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">悼襄王</span>去世。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十三年</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕太子丹\">丹（燕太子丹）</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>为<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">质</span>，逃归<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十五年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">韩王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩安\">安（韩安）</span>，设置<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川郡</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十七年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵迁\">迁（赵迁）</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>公子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵嘉\">嘉（赵嘉）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">自立</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">代王</span>。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "22.1": {
      "title": "荆轲刺秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>即将<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵已临<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">易水</span>，祸患将要到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕太子丹\">丹（燕太子丹）</span>暗中供养<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十人</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荆轲</span>献<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">督亢</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">地图</span>给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，借机<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">袭刺</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王察觉，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：荆轲\">轲（荆轲）</span>，派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王翦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十九年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>我国<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓟</span>都，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span>出逃，迁居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕太子丹\">丹（燕太子丹）</span>献给<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。"
    },
    "22.2": {
      "title": "秦灭燕",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十三年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">燕王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬喜\">喜（姬喜）</span>，最终<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>。这一年，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王贲</span>也<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">代王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：赵嘉\">嘉（赵嘉）</span>。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "（本段内容在以下子段中。）"
    },
    "23.1": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公奭</span>可以称得上仁德了！甘棠树尚被思念，何况他本人呢？<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>国迫近<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮貉</span>，向内夹在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>之间，艰难地生存于强国之间，是最为弱小的，几乎被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>的情形有好几次。然而社稷血食延续了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八九百岁</span>，在<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姬姓</span>诸侯国中是最后灭亡的，这岂不是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召公</span>功业的余荫吗！"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "赞诗",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">召伯</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相</span>，分管<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陕</span>而治。 人们感念他的恩德，思念<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">甘棠</span>。 庄公护送霸主，惠公沉溺宠姬。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文公</span>听从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人之言，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">苏秦</span>施展辞令。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">易王</span>刚即位，齐宣王来欺凌。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬哙\">哙（姬哙）</span>无道，禅位给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子之</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：燕昭王\">昭王（燕昭王）</span>礼待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，志在报复<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临淄</span>。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">督亢</span>之谋不成，终被秦所芟夷。"
    }
  }
}